日本为中心的。尽管日本的人口只有美国的三分之一，但日本的日活跃用户数量与美国的日活跃用户数量大致相同。」（澎湃新闻）马斯克：不裁了，开始招，推特不应只以美国为中心 _ 未来 2%_ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-eb05fd041c5e25910b9e72f365c1993a_qhd.jpg?source=4e949a73"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "122 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/568181594"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8ei7iMq0pa0HEAMaCDg4NTQ0ODkxIPDw8ZsGMBI46AJADnIJNTY4MTgxNTk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1669194534.800815", "card_id": "Q_555254864", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 124}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么唐僧在大唐看不到妖怪，出了大唐满地都是妖怪呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-7252dba06786860f62601522be28588e_qhd.jpg?source=4e949a73"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/555254864"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8ei7iMq0pa0HEAMaCDg1NjcyODg0IN2ZuZkGMAc4sgFAD3IJNTU1MjU0ODY0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1669194534.8014026", "card_id": "Q_568189551", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价十月新番《电锯人》第七集？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-072dbcaeed31e7a170ab87e13f8d9126_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/568189551"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8ei7iMq0pa0HEAMaCDg4NTQ2NjM5IJyN8psGMAI4JkAQcgk1NjgxODk1NTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type"